299
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:16,360
Mr. Veerawat, have you ever
analyzed this phrase?

300
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:19,600
When one business grows,
another one collapses.

301
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:21,680
