505
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:16,800
Honestly,

506
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:21,640
someone like him never got mad at anyone.

507
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:25,440
He was incredibly patient.

508
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:29,040
